sources.title: The Gypsy Moon (1954) ROCKY JONES, SPACE RANGER
sources.description:
ars: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield
Director: Hollingsworth Morse

You've heard of The Lone Ranger, now meet The Space Ranger!

Follow the adventures of Rocky Jones and crew as they cruise the galaxy in their Orbit Jet X-V2 and defend Earth against space-bound evil doers!

metadata.Plot: Rocky Jones discovers two strange moons orbiting each other, inhabited by warring civilizations.
metadata.Actors: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield
